column12: ['Courtesy of its inbuilt dual microphones and AI, the Dell Inspiron 7420 14 Two-in-one Laptop offers clear audio while minimising background noise. And, thanks to its Waves MaxxAudio Pro, this laptop ensures clear and loud audio. Moreover, its mechanical camera privacy shutters give you peace of mind when you need to disconnect.', None, 'Owing to its high-quality FHD+ display with an up to 16:10 aspect ratio, this laptop offers engrossing visual performance. And, featuring ComfortView software, this laptop minimises the damaging blue light emissions along with DC dimming to decrease flicker and offer prolonged screen time without straining your eyes.', None, 'Courtesy of its up to 360-degree hinge, this laptop allows you to work in up to four different modes. Also, with a lift hinge, this laptop ensures that your wrist stays comfortable when you type or chat. And, sporting a large touchpad, this laptop gives you additional space for navigation. Moreover, its edge-to-edge mylar material stretches in the entire palm rest and touchpad, thereby offering a contemporary and smooth work surface. Besides, with an active pen, this laptop allows you to write naturally and precisely without any pairing.', None, 'Powered by a 12th Gen Intel Core i5 processor, this laptop facilitates exceptional performance. Also, its lid-open sensor allows you to activate the laptop simply by opening it, even if it is inactive or in hibernation. Moreover, with its fingerprint reader, this laptop can verify identity for login in no time by making use of Windows Hello.', None, 'As this laptop comes with a USB Type-C power adapter, it is sleek and allows you to carry it with ease. Also, owing to its ExpressCharge, this laptop lets you charge it in a jiffy.', None]

column11: ["Whether it is for work, school, or day-to-day computing requirements, the Dell Inspiron 3511 11th Gen Core i3 Laptop is a must-have. It offers quick response time and silent performance, thanks to this laptop's 11th Gen Intel Core i3 processor and dual drive SSD and HDD options. In addition, it has a spacious keyboard with a numeric keypad, large keycaps, and a large touchpad that facilitates easy navigation. Moreover, you can work comfortably on this laptop as it features a lift hinge that raises it to an ergonomic angle and offers a comfortable typing angle.", "Whether it is for work, school, or day-to-day computing requirements, the Dell Inspiron 3511 11th Gen Core i3 Laptop is a must-have. It offers quick response time and silent performance, thanks to this laptop's 11th Gen Intel Core i3 processor and dual drive SSD and HDD options. In addition, it has a spacious keyboard with a numeric keypad, large keycaps, and a large touchpad that facilitates easy navigation. column12: ['Sporting an 11th Gen Intel Core i3 processor and dual drive SSD and HDD options, the Dell Inspiron 3511 11th Gen Core i3 Laptop provides a high response rate and silent performance. In addition, it features a wide keyboard with a numeric keypad, large keycaps, and a large touchpad that makes it easy to navigate your tasks. Moreover, if you want to continue working in low-light settings, you can opt for a backlit keyboard upgrade. Besides, you can work comfortably with a lift hinge that raises your laptop to an ergonomic angle and offers a comfortable typing angle. Boasting Dell ComfortView Low Blue Light (LBL) solutions, this laptop reduces harmful blue light emissions and enhances eye comfort during extended use. Furthermore, this 39.624 cm (15.6) laptop with narrow borders on three sides offers more screen space for an engrossing FHD viewing experience.', None, "Featuring an inbuilt HD webcam, this laptop facilitates hassle-free connection and enhances your virtual appearance. Additionally, this laptop's small rubber feet and bumpers on the hinge keep it from sliding and add stability when placed on hard surfaces, ensuring long-lasting durability.", None, 'The use of post-consumer recycled polymers in this laptop contributes to its sustainability and eco-friendly design. All painted parts of this laptop are painted with low VOC (Volatile Organic Compounds) waterborne paint, making it even more environment-friendly.', None, 'Thanks to its ExpressCharge capabilities, this laptop reduces the amount of time it needs to be plugged in and can recharge its battery to up to 80% in 60 minutes.', None]

column12: ['Powered by the AMD Ryzen Mobile Processor, the Dell G-15 gaming laptop offers an enthralling performance while playing games and streaming videos. column12: ['Featuring up to 11th Generation Intel Core i7 processor, the Dell G15-5511 Gaming Laptop allows seamless gaming and lets you watch videos, movies, and more without interruptions. column10: ['Dell International Service Pvt Ltd']
column12: ["Featuring an AMD Ryzen 5000 H-Series Mobile Processor, the Dell G15-5515 Gaming Laptop delivers impressive performance for gaming as well as content streaming. With the help of their copper piping, this laptop's thermal systems dissipate heat as it is drawn through the keyboard's top and bottom and expelled through up to four sizable exhaust vents. The sophisticated thermal design of this laptop offers your system additional thermal headroom to generate enough power while adapting to fluctuating system loads. As a result, component temperatures are kept low and clock speeds can continue to be high for a long period of time. Besides, more storage translates into a quicker startup time, so you can immediately begin playing games. Furthermore, integrated with Killer Wi-Fi 6 AX1650 (2x2) technology, which supports Bluetooth 5.2 and offers data rates of up to 2.4 Gbps and improved network capacity, this laptop ensures quick uploads and downloads, low latency, and long battery life.", None, 'This laptop has an NVIDIA GeForce RTX 3050 graphics card, which uses the 2nd Gen RTX architecture, NVIDIA Ampere, which has new RT Cores, Tensor Cores, and streaming multiprocessors enabling powerful AI capabilities and realistic ray-traced images. Besides, with up to 4 GB GDDR6 of dedicated memory, this laptop allows you to experience the power-packed action with rapid loading times and a silent system. In addition, the FHD resolution and high refresh rates of this laptop make gaming rapid, seamless, and detailed.', None, 'Featuring a sturdy finish, this laptop is easy to maintain. So, it is an ideal addition to your gaming setup.', None, "Integrated with the Game Shift technology, this laptop ensures powerful performance as per the demands of intense gaming. In the Alienware Command Centre, when the Fn key and the Game Shift key are pressed simultaneously, Game Shift gets activated, which boosts fan performance and keeps your system cool while the processors are working hard. Thanks to this laptop's dual speakers and Nahimic 3D Audio for gaming, you can hear attack techniques with utmost clarity. Moreover, the Alienware Command Centre's WASD controls and an orange-backlit keyboard make it possible to play games clearly even in low-light conditions. Moreover, built with an up to 56 Wh battery, this laptop allows for quick charge, so you won't have to rely on a socket to play your favourite games.", None, "Boasting high-performance software designed specifically to improve your gameplay, this laptop can personalise all of your system and game settings, fix problems, and manage gaming duration. Additionally, this laptop's hardware and software environments are under your control. In addition to customising the hardware for each game you play, you can also alter the environment and setup to make your software feel and look exactly how you want it to without affecting your gameplay or other tasks. Also, this laptop's Ace library science, an easy-to-use interface that links all of your system settings with a gaming library, makes it hassle-free to obtain gaming-related information. Regardless of the source, this laptop's command centre lets you quickly access your games and customise their settings. So, no matter where you launch the game, your customised profile will remain exactly the way you set it up.", None]
